snippet.title: Evercade - Sunsoft Collection 2 - Trailer
snippet.description:
Sunsoft returns to Evercade with a selection of 7 big hits and cult classics. Includes Ufouria: The Saga, Blaster Master: Enemy Below, Aero the Acro-Bat 2, Zero the Kamikaze Squirrel, Daze Before Christmas, Galaxy Fight: Universal Warriors and the first localised release of Pri Pri Primitive Princess!

Pre-order February 29th
Releases April 2024

Cartridge: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/sunsoft-collection-2/
Website: Evercade.co.uk
